title: Rancakkan Madani reflects govt's commitment to transparency, says PM’s aide
description: PETALING JAYA: The Rancakkan Madani Bersama Malaysiaku programme reflects the Madani government's commitment to transparent annual reporting as it enters its third year, said the Prime Minister's senior press secretary, Tunku Nashrul Abaidah. Read full story
